{"prompt": "Generate a website for a e-commerce store. The website should be user-friendly and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>E-Commerce Store</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #e57373;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #d32f2f, #ef9a9a);\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n            color: #b71c1c;\n        }\n        .products-section {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n        .products-section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 25px;\n        }\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .product-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n        .product-info {\n            padding: 15px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        .product-info h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .product-info p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n        .price {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #000000;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-button {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 15px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 0 auto 10px auto;\n        }\n        .add-to-cart-button:hover {\n            background-color: #b71c1c;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #e57373;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Basic Responsive Adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .product-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n            }\n            .product-info h4 {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .products-section h3 {\n                font-size: 1.7em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>StyleSphere</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#home\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"home\" class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Discover Your Next Style Essential</h2>\n        <p>High-quality fashion and accessories curated just for you. Shop the latest trends and timeless classics.</p>\n        <a href=\"#products\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"products\" class=\"products-section container\">\n        <h3>Featured Products</h3>\n        <div class=\"product-grid\">\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d32f2f/ffffff?text=Product+1\" alt=\"Product 1\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Elegant Red Dress</h4>\n                    <p>A sophisticated red dress perfect for any occasion. Made with premium fabric.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$89.99</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e57373/ffffff?text=Product+2\" alt=\"Product 2\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Classic Leather Wallet</h4>\n                    <p>A minimalist and durable leather wallet with multiple card slots.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$45.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f44336/ffffff?text=Product+3\" alt=\"Product 3\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Stylish Sunglasses</h4>\n                    <p>UV-protective sunglasses with a sleek, modern design. Available in various colors.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$65.50</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"product-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ef9a9a/ffffff?text=Product+4\" alt=\"Product 4\">\n                <div class=\"product-info\">\n                    <h4>Comfortable Sneakers</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight and breathable sneakers, ideal for everyday wear and light workouts.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$72.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"add-to-cart-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: center; padding: 40px 0;\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #d32f2f;\">About Us</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n            Welcome to StyleSphere, your premier destination for fashion-forward apparel and accessories. We are passionate about providing our customers with high-quality products that blend style, comfort, and durability. Our mission is to help you express your unique personality through carefully selected pieces.\n        </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\" style=\"text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; background-color: #f0f0f0;\">\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 2em; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #d32f2f;\">Get in Touch</h3>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.6;\">\n            Have questions or need assistance? Feel free to reach out to us.<br>\n            Email: <a href=\"mailto:support@stylesphere.com\">support@stylesphere.com</a><br>\n            Phone: (123) 456-7890\n        </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 StyleSphere. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Designed with <span style=\"color: #d32f2f;\">&#10084;</span></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for interactivity, if needed in the future.\n        // For this simple site, it's mostly for structure.\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}